          <p>
            When I'm not working with you - I spin up my little side projects:
            <%= link_to 'Complete Food', 'https://completefood.guru/', class: 'link' %>,
            <%= link_to 'Moonbeat', 'https://moonbeat.io/', class: 'link' %>,
            <%= link_to 'WeedTalks', 'https://weedtalks.io/', class: 'link' %>,
            <%= link_to 'Baby Sitting Bordeaux', 'https://babysittingbordeaux.fr/', class: 'link' %>
